<view style="padding: 40rpx;">
  <text style="font-size: 48rpx; font-weight: bold; color: #e84393; text-align: center; display: block; margin-bottom: 40rpx;">脱口秀金句</text>
  
  <view style="background: #fff; border-radius: 24rpx; padding: 32rpx; margin-bottom: 24rpx;">
    <text style="font-size: 28rpx; color: #e84393; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 20rpx; display: block;">—— 李诞</text>
    <text style="font-size: 32rpx; color: #333; line-height: 1.6; display: block;">我小时候家里穷，我妈给我买了一双耐克鞋，我穿了三个月才发现是"耐克"</text>
    <text style="font-size: 24rpx; color: #999; text-align: right; display: block;">《吐槽大会》</text>
  </view>
  
  <view style="background: #fff; border-radius: 24rpx; padding: 32rpx; margin-bottom: 24rpx;">
    <text style="font-size: 28rpx; color: #e84393; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 20rpx; display: block;">—— 王建国</text>
    <text style="font-size: 32rpx; color: #333; line-height: 1.6; display: block;">我太敏感了，别人关门声音大一点，我都会觉得他在说"你好胖"</text>
    <text style="font-size: 24rpx; color: #999; text-align: right; display: block;">《脱口秀大会》</text>
  </view>
  
  <view style="background: #fff; border-radius: 24rpx; padding: 32rpx; margin-bottom: 24rpx;">
    <text style="font-size: 28rpx; color: #e84393; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 20rpx; display: block;">—— 杨笠</text>
    <text style="font-size: 32rpx; color: #333; line-height: 1.6; display: block;">我问我妈："妈，我是不是长得很丑？"我妈说："你照镜子的时候，镜子没碎就说明你还行"</text>
    <text style="font-size: 24rpx; color: #999; text-align: right; display: block;">《脱口秀大会》</text>
  </view>
</view>